&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;00000080:00200000:0.0:1459365868.977899:0:62879:0:(namei.c:527:ll_lookup_it()) VFS Op:name=vr014.hdf,dir=144115238826934470/33554443(ffff88061af76678),intent=open
&lt;/pre&gt;
